          	  <a href="artical-src12165.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12165.htm">教示小兒ー積成在佇家庭 [ KÀ-SĪ SIÁU-JÎーCHEK-SÊNG CHĀI TĪ KA-TÊNG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">教示小兒
積成在佇家庭
 
<span s...<a href="artical-12165.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
